sentences.english: Put the clothes into the dryer when you get home.
sentences.chinese: 到家後就把衣服放進乾衣機裏。

sentences.english: If Fred didn't leave till five o'clock, he can't be home yet.
sentences.chinese: 如果弗雷德五點鐘以後走護短，現在還不可能到家。

sentences.english: I don't know how long I'll have to play and practice before I can gain that kind of skills.
sentences.chinese: 這樣的絕活不知道要練多久才能到家和隨心應手？

sentences.english: The tired children don't get home until 7:00.
sentences.chinese: 疲憊不堪的孩子們要道晚上7點才能到家。

sentences.english: When I got back to my apartment, I heard the water running. My wife was in the shower.
sentences.chinese: 到家後，我聽見浴室裏有水流聲，是我老婆在洗澡。
我們週日早上一點半到家。

sentences.english: They were not welcomed home very  cordially by their mother.
sentences.chinese: 到家以後，母親並不怎麼熱誠地歡迎她們。

sentences.english: They thought the wonton soup and milky coffee combination was hilarious.
sentences.chinese: 寶釵和黛玉覺得餛飩湯和奶咖啡的搭配滑稽到家了。

sentences.english: I often walk the 3 mi. home from work rather than take the subway.
sentences.chinese: 從公司到家，有三公里，我都是步行回往，不坐地鐵。

sentences.english: I will be home after across this tunnel.
sentences.chinese: 過了這個小洞子，就馬上到家了。

sentences.english: This evening, I found my daughter doing homework in the computer-room after I was home.
sentences.chinese: 今天晚上到家後，發現女兒在電腦房做功課。

sentences.english: Before Willem got home, the phone rang.
sentences.chinese: 威廉還沒有到家，電話就響了。

sentences.english: I have the highest opinion in the world of Edward's heart.
sentences.chinese: 我對愛德華的那顆心算是佩服到家了。

sentences.english: But he also knew where she'd be likely to go on the way home from the mall.
sentences.chinese: 但是，他又想，在從購物中心到家的路上也很有可能。

sentences.english: Chain to implement unified prices, the establishment of customer files at home.
sentences.chinese: 實行連鎖經營，統一售價，建立顧客檔案服務到家。

sentences.english: The westerner thought that leaves behind the address to the human, must ask opposite party to sojourn proficiently .
sentences.chinese: 西方人認爲給人留下住址，就得請對方到家作客。
